        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate leading-relaxed">
          All keystroke monitoring, logs, and diagnostic activities take place solely within your browser memory. No keystrokes are transmitted, uploaded, or analyzed by external APIs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>


