          <li><strong>Real-time state lookup:</strong> Evaluates modifiers directly from actual key interactions to show true software activation.</li>
          <li><strong>Focus Restoration Check:</strong> Monitors the browser tab's visibility and focus state, re-synchronizing modifier indicators instantly on the next interaction if changes occurred while unfocused.</li>
